{"id":493128245,"lang":"cpp","time":"3 weeks, 4 days","timestamp":1621012556,"status_display":"Runtime Error","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/493128245/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Ugly Number II","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int nthUglyNumber(int n) {\n        priority_queue<int,vector<int>,greater<>> minq;\n        minq.push(1);\n        if(n==0) return 1;\n        int cnt =1;\n        while(cnt<n){\n            int temp = minq.top();\n            minq.pop();\n            if(temp%2==0){\n                minq.push(temp*2);\n            } else if(temp%3==0){\n                minq.push(temp*2);\n                minq.push(temp*3);\n            } else{\n                minq.push(temp*2);\n                minq.push(temp*3);\n                minq.push(temp*5);\n            }\n            cnt++;\n        }\n        return minq.top();\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"ugly-number-ii"}
